- `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775505238315-2ltw9f/packages/shared/src/theme.ts` (new -- theme types and built-in definitions)
- `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775505238315-2ltw9f/apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts` (rewrite -- core theme engine)
